    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/1927"
                            >Radelchis</persName> Dei providencia gentis Longobardorum <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, per rogum <persName key="#Intercessory"
                            ref="#people/1936">Garichise</persName> dilecte nostre sororis, tibi
                            <persName key="#Prevosts" ref="#people/1937">Adelperto</persName>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">preposito</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Prevosts #Landed_possessions #Wood #Angaria #Census #Tolls" ref="#juridical_persons/1901">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName> de <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/2301">Loco
                            Sano</placeName> eundem monasterium, quod subiectum esse videtur <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/1900">Sancti
                            Vincencii</orgName> in tali racione illud concedimus tibi, sicut per
                        legale iudicium illud <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1926"
                            >Maio</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> vicit, et recollegit presencia domne <persName
                            key="#Queen" ref="#people/91">Ageltrude</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">imperatricis</rs>, simul eciam et nostra presencia,ut liber
                        sit ab omni <rs key="#Angaria">angaria</rs>, et <rs key="#Census"
                            >pensione</rs>, sive <rs key="#Tolls">portatico</rs>, cum offertis, et
                        libertis, et cum commenditis suis, tam cum hiis, quos modo habet, quam quos
                        in antea habere potuerit, et cum ipsa <rs key="#Landed_possessions #Wood"
                            >fracta</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Wood #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/2322">Sancti Felicis</placeName>, que in territorio eiusdem
                        monasterii constructa est. Quicquid inde vobis legibus pertinet, et omnia
                        que ibi a nostris antecessoribus, et nobilibus hominibus data sunt, ut amodo
                        et deinceps in vestra sit potestate et dominacione firmiter per hoc nostrum
                        roboratum preceptum; et neque a nobis, neque a nullis ex nostris iudicibus,
                        comitibus, castaldeis, vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam
                        requisicionem; sed perpetuis temporibus in vestra pemaneat potestate et
                        dominacione laborandi, regendi, gubernandi, et exinde quicquid utile fuerit
                        faciendi. Quod vero <rs key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma">preceptum
                            concessionis</rs>, ex iussione predicte potestatis, scripsi ego
                        <persName key="#Notary #Deacons"><name ref="Ermengardus">Ermengardus</name>
                        </persName><rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs> superius dicte gloriose
                        potestatis. <date>Actum in <placeName ref="#places/110"
                                >Benevento</placeName> septimo anno imperii domni <persName
                                key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/136">Lamberti</persName>
                            <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatoris</rs> augusti, et secundo anno
                            principatus post restauracionem eiusdem domini nostri gloriosi
                            principis, mense augusto, prima indiccione</date>.</ab>
                </div>
